Global Keyboard Tray Market Insights
Keyboard Tray Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Keyboard Tray Market Overview
The global keyboard tray market was valued at USD 1.35 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.2% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing need for ergonomic solutions in office and home workspaces to prevent musculoskeletal disorders. The market is witnessing increased demand for adjustable and customizable keyboard trays that offer comfort and enhance productivity. Additionally, rising awareness about ergonomics and the growth in remote work culture are major contributors to the demand. North America is expected to hold the largest market share, followed by Europe and Asia Pacific.

